title: Encoding data from PDF file into Excel spreadsheet
snippet:
I am looking to hire a talented associate to encode all the data from the collection of PDF files into a single, well organized, Microsoft Excel document.

Original PDF data (15 documents):

https://www.dropbox.com/sh/0c65qj7pp0jf5tu/AADBZH4wXWdtToS5NPpSDG50a?dl=0

Data must be encoded with 100% accuracy.

Very happy to leave perfect 5 star feedback for high quality work.
